# Firewall tenant registry — runtime SQLite created when the dashboard
# imports with the default AXIOM_FIREWALL_TENANT_DIR=tenants.  Real
# deploys point this at /data/tenants via env; this directory only ever
# exists when tests/imports run from the repo root.
tenants/
